00:21:48.540 --> 00:21:49.730
So you'll see circles.

00:21:49.730 --> 00:21:50.780
You'll see squares.

00:21:50.780 --> 00:21:51.710
You'll see rectangles.

00:21:51.710 --> 00:21:54.520
You'll see basically
divisions of space.

00:21:54.520 --> 00:21:58.810
So when you want to have a
contained element the simplest

00:21:58.810 --> 00:22:02.230
way to do that is to
